OL,3,CWater industry review unlikely to
OL,4,Cspark required change, claims Feargal
OL,5,CSharkey
OL,7,FWater campaigner Feargal Sharkey says
OL,8,Fhe believes a landmark review into the
OL,9,Fwater industry will not produce
OL,10,Fchanges the public and customers
OL,11,Fdesperately need.
OL,13,FThe Independent Water Commission, led
OL,14,Fby former Bank of England deputy
OL,15,Fgovernor Sir Jon Cunliffe, will
OL,16,Foutline recommendations to turn around
OL,17,Fthe floundering sector in its final
OL,18,Freport on Monday, with claims it will
OL,19,Flead to the abolition of embattled
OL,20,Fwater regulator Ofwat.
