OL,3,CWater industry review unlikely to
OL,4,Cspark required change, claims Feargal
OL,5,CSharkey
OL,7,FBut former Undertones frontman
OL,8,FSharkey, who has become a leading
OL,9,Fcampaigner for water companies to
OL,10,Fclean up their act, said he fears the
OL,11,Fhighly anticipated report will be a
OL,12,F"flat pancake".
OL,14,FHe told the PA news agency: "We were
OL,15,Fpromised that the report will bring us
OL,16,Fchampagne ` but it will just be a
OL,17,Fsaucer of milk."
