OL,3,CWater industry review unlikely to
OL,4,Cspark required change, claims Feargal
OL,5,CSharkey
OL,7,FSharkey, who has given evidence to MPs
OL,8,Fon the need for reform and has spoken
OL,9,Fat numerous public and trade union
OL,10,Fmeetings, said he does not believe
OL,11,F"much will happen" as a result of the
OL,12,Freport's findings.
OL,14,F"Sir Jon's job is to make the current
OL,15,Fsystem better, but so many things have
OL,16,Fnot been considered in his review,
OL,17,Fsuch as the ownership of the water
OL,18,Fcompanies.
