OL,7,FHe believes the public and customers
OL,8,Fhave been treated with "contempt" by
OL,9,Fwater companies for years despite
OL,10,Foutrage over sewage pollution of
OL,11,Frivers and waterways.
OL,13,FHe added the fact that the review had
OL,14,Fbeen held was a victory for the many
OL,15,Fsmall community groups across the
OL,16,Fcountry set up to tackle the crisis.
