OL,3,CWater industry review unlikely to
OL,4,Cspark required change, claims Feargal
OL,5,CSharkey
OL,7,FThe review was commissioned by the UK
OL,8,Fand Welsh governments as part of their
OL,9,Fresponse to systemic industry
OL,10,Ffailures, which include rising bills,
OL,11,Frecord sewage spills and debt-ridden
OL,12,Fcompany finances, although ministers
OL,13,Fhave ruled out nationalising companies.
OL,15,FA Government spokesperson pointed out
OL,16,Fthat unfair bonuses have been banned
OL,17,Ffor senior executives at six water
OL,18,Fcompanies under new measures which
OL,19,Fcame into force last month.
