OL,3,CWater industry review unlikely to
OL,4,Cspark required change, claims Feargal
OL,5,CSharkey
OL,7,FThe Government said at the time that
OL,8,Ftransformative change across the water
OL,9,Fsector was needed to clean up rivers,
OL,10,Flakes and seas, and modernise the
OL,11,Fsector for decades to come.
OL,13,FUnder the rules, companies are not
OL,14,Fpermitted to pay bonuses to water
OL,15,Fbosses that oversee poor environmental
OL,16,Fand customer outcomes.
